      framework and terminology.
   c. Linking to this repository.
   d. Quoting short excerpts with attribution to the source.
   e. Introducing or referencing the Work in articles, videos, newsletters,
      forums, or social media.

3. Prohibited without prior written permission
   a. Presenting the framework, in whole or in part, as one's own original
